---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="The $58 Million Project | Case Study | Wet Dog Drones"
  description="16 months of bi-weekly progress flights on a $58 million construction project. 85-second time-lapse showing 14 months of progress.">

  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
        <span class="bg-blue-600 text-white text-sm font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded">16 MONTHS</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">The $58 Million Project</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300">14 months of progress compressed into 85 seconds.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Duration</div>
          <div class="font-semibold">16 Months</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Location</div>
          <div class="font-semibold">Severance, Colorado</div>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-sm text-slate-500">Flight Schedule</div>
          <div class="font-semibold">Bi-weekly → Monthly</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">The Project</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
        A $58 million construction project that demanded documentation from groundbreaking through closeout. Starting in March 2024 and continuing through August 2026, Wet Dog Drones provided continuous progress monitoring that kept the project timeline visible and accountable.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">The Schedule</h2>
      
      <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Active Construction Phase</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600">Bi-weekly flights from groundbreaking until dried in</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Drying In</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600">Once the roof was on and building dried in, flights scaled back to monthly</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0">3</div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-semibold">Interior Finishes</div>
            <div class="text-slate-600">Monthly documentation through final punch list and closeout</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">The Deliverables</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">📊 Progress Data</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
            <li>✓ Orthomosaics at each flight interval</li>
            <li>✓ Timeline comparisons (week-over-week)</li>
            <li>✓ Change detection analysis</li>
            <li>✓ Volumetric calculations for earthwork</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">🎥 Visual Deliverables</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600">
            <li>✓ 85-second time-lapse video</li>
            <li>✓ 3D flythroughs</li>
            <li>✓ Marketing footage for stakeholders</li>
            <li>✓ Custom angles on request</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-600 p-6 my-8">
        <blockquote class="text-xl italic text-blue-900">
          "85 seconds that shows 14 months of progress. That's the power of consistent documentation."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">The Value</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
        Progress documentation isn't just about having pretty videos. It's about accountability, timeline management, and stakeholder communication.
      </p>

      <ul class="space-y-3 text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8">
        <li>✓ Catch delays before they become critical</li>
        <li>✓ Document weather-related stoppages</li>
        <li>✓ Verify subcontractor progress claims</li>
        <li>✓ Provide visual updates to owners and investors</li>
        <li>✓ Create marketing content for future projects</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 mt-12">The Timeline Compression</h2>
      
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
        14 months of bi-weekly flights equals roughly 30 separate data captures. Each capture included hundreds of photos, processed into orthomosaics with high-precision accuracy. The result: an 85-second time-lapse that shows the entire transformation from empty lot to completed building.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-6">
        It's one thing to tell stakeholders the project is on track. It's another thing to show them — compressed into a minute and a half that tells the whole story.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-amber-50 rounded-lg border border-amber-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-2">Have a Long-Term Project?</h3>
        <p class="text-amber-800 mb-4">
          Multi-phase or long-duration projects benefit most from progress monitoring. Let's talk about a flight schedule that matches your construction timeline.
        </p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-amber-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-amber-700 transition">
          Get a Quote
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">More Case Studies</h2>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <a href="/case-studies/severance-library" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">$40,000 SAVED</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Severance Library</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Pre-construction baseline documentation split an $80K change order in half.</p>
        </a>

        <a href="/case-studies/clear-creek-schools" class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <div class="text-green-600 font-bold text-sm mb-2">$400,000 SAVED</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Clear Creek Schools</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">Interior documentation proved building was empty before construction.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
